This is a simple page to generate an oauth token for the Twitch.tv IRC.

To connect to the IRC pass the oauth token as a password to the server.
Example in WeeChat:

/server add twitch irc.twitch.tv/6667 -password=oauth:23456yufgd45trgf4354t -nicks=MyNick
/connect twitch


This page can be viewed at: https://shawn-smith.github.io/twitchtokengen/